title: STL Super Fire Extra Long Safety Matches - 15cm Matches for Wood Burners, BBQs, Fire Pits, Stoves & More - 65 Matches per Box - Premium Quality & Safe Ignition (12 BOXES)
features: EXTRA LONG 15CM SAFETY MATCHES - Designed to reach where others can't, these extra-long matches are perfect for lighting wood burners, chimineas, fire pits, campfires, stoves, and even delicate candles, without burning your fingers.

SUITABLE FOR ALL FIRES - Whether you're igniting a hard-to-reach briquette or charcoal BBQ, or firing up a kitchen oven or gas range top, these extra-long fire starters allow you extra time to safely ignite multiple flames at once.

SAFE & EASY TO LIGHT - Say goodbye to struggling with awkward lighters. STL's high-quality matches are crafted for durability and reliability, ensuring a smooth and consistent strike every time, so you can ignite with confidence.

COMPACT & CONVENIENT - The neatly designed matchbox makes storage and stacking easy, fitting perfectly in drawers or on mantels. With a striking surface on the side, they are ideal for igniting fires effortlessly.

PREMIUM QUALITY & QUANTITY - Each box contains 65 high-quality, 15cm long matches. STL Super Fire Sticks prioritize user safety with their extended length and secure packaging, making them an essential for any fire lighting needs.
